props.name: canActivate
props.desc: True if this item can be visually activated (defaults to true)

props.name: icon
props.desc: The path to an icon to display in this menu item (defaults to Roo.BLANK_IMAGE_URL)

props.name: itemCls
props.desc: The default CSS class to use for menu items (defaults to "x-menu-item")

props.name: showDelay
props.desc: Length of time in milliseconds to wait before showing this item (defaults to 200)
